  "stem": "<p>The table below gives some values of the function <em>g</em>.</p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"6\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse\">\n<tr><th><em>x</em></th><th><em>g</em>(<em>x</em>)</th></tr>\n<tr><td>0</td><td>3</td></tr>\n<tr><td>1</td><td>6</td></tr>\n<tr><td>2</td><td>12</td></tr>\n<tr><td>3</td><td>24</td></tr>\n</table>\n<p>Which of the following equations could define <em>g</em>?</p>",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p><em>g</em>(<em>x</em>) = 3(2<sup><em>x</em></sup>)</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": "b",
      "content": "<p><em>g</em>(<em>x</em>) = 3(2<sup>&minus;<em>x</em></sup>)</p>"
